What you need to know:

Tusker attackers then resorted to long range shots, but Oyemba denied them to keep Leopards' lead intact.Kipyegon would make a goal line clearance from a Macharia's strike in the 86th minute and Meja blew a late chance in the added time, shooting to the clouds as Leopards held on to record their second win over Tusker this season after beating them 2-1 in the league in November 2020.